Name: LabRat
About the game: Abandoned Lab, Reset Power, RUN! A point and click game of surviving an abandoned lab, discovering it's secrets while surviving the creature within. Explore many different rooms in the lab to discover the downfall of the Lab. Complete Puzzles that will help you get to new places in the Lab. Run from the creature that is searching for you.
